data.description: Here's your chance to own a charming remodeled condo in the heart of the Biltmore area! The home boasts gorgeous upgrades throughout from quartz counters to a luxurious bathroom, barn doors, soothing colors, and more! Relax on your corner-unit balcony with beautiful mountain views! Enjoy the community amenities such as the pool and gym, plus the convenience of near by walking trails! Walk to the grocery store, restaurants and more just steps from the complex!
